                       Network.IRC.Bot
                       Network.IRC.Bot.BotMonad
                       Network.IRC.Bot.Core
                       Network.IRC.Bot.Commands
                       Network.IRC.Bot.ErrorCodes
                       Network.IRC.Bot.Log
                       Network.IRC.Bot.Part.Channels
